(498, 0, 0, 1, 0, '2010-02-07 22:48:00', 1, 'BR', '2012', 'Political Science', 'Brian', 'Waswani', 'Odhiambo', '654219', 'Nairobi', '', '0500', 'Kenya', '2039090254', '', '', '201190', 'New Haven', 'CT', '06520', '', 'Se', '908001543', 'brian.odhiambo@yale.edu', 'brian.odhiambo@yale.edu', 0, 'Kenya', 'Student', '', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Black or African American', '', 'Music is my passion. I have been DJing for about four years and hosting a radio show on WYBC will be the epitome of my DJ experience which I would hold with great reverence. Having deejayed at Yale, I believe I have had a sense of what people like to listen to and what needs to be improved upon. Through WYBC, I believe I am able to address one key area that needs to be focused on, music diversity.  \n\nHaving gone throught the WYBC shows and having listened to many of the shows broadcasted, I noticed that Africa was a bit underrepresented.  It goes without saying that little is known of contemporary African music on Yale''s campus as evidenced by the lack of such music on DJ playlists at parties and other events. The stereotypical perception of African music as the beating of drums, blowing of horns and people dancing in costumes could not be further from the truth. I wish to bring into the WYBC family a contemporary African music show. I have extensive knowledge of up to date African Hip Hop, R&B, Dancehall, Rock among other genres of music and have access to this music on a regular basis. I believe that this music together with my DJ experience before and at Yale, will draw a big audience owing to the large coverage provided by WYBC. I plan on alternating between live mix sessions, prerecorded digitally mixed sessions and guest mixes in order to diversify the shows thereby adding to their appeal.\n\nI believe that WYBC will be a great and fun learning experience for me. I am strongly committed to learning what will be taught to me as well as meeting all the expectations that will be required of me. If selected for the training I believe that I will not dissapoint.\n\n', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
